    "description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Your Numbers Carefully</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331680/extras/f053e099da05cd5e3b8475d3238dbf1b.poster.avif?t=1756236398\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331680/extras/f053e099da05cd5e3b8475d3238dbf1b.webm?t=1756236398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331680/extras/f053e099da05cd5e3b8475d3238dbf1b.mp4?t=1756236398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>-Collecting as many numbers as possible will maximize your score. Analyze all numbers on the screen to determine the most efficient order to grab as many numbers as possible.</i><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fast forward to speed up the game or move unwanted numbers out of the way.</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331680/extras/55394c41c573de9f7561234c883e7b58.poster.avif?t=1756236398\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331680/extras/55394c41c573de9f7561234c883e7b58.webm?t=1756236398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331680/extras/55394c41c573de9f7561234c883e7b58.mp4?t=1756236398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>-Fast forwarding the game can help speed up the flow of early rounds in repeated runs or speed up your down time between rounds, if you are daring enough..</i><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use BOMBS to clear all numbers on screen to save yourself from certain death.</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331680/extras/57d412cd3c021ce03414b89c402af35a.poster.avif?t=1756236398\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331680/extras/57d412cd3c021ce03414b89c402af35a.webm?t=1756236398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331680/extras/57d412cd3c021ce03414b89c402af35a.mp4?t=1756236398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>-If you are in danger of being hit by a number you don't need and there is nowhere save to move, you can destroy all numbers on the screen by using a bomb. Keep in mind you only have 3 of these. Conserve your ammo...</i><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Think quickly, collect an incorrect number and it is instant game over.</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331680/extras/a1dc2e668029e36048f36fe0528ed95d.poster.avif?t=1756236398\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331680/extras/a1dc2e668029e36048f36fe0528ed95d.webm?t=1756236398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331680/extras/a1dc2e668029e36048f36fe0528ed95d.mp4?t=1756236398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>-Remember you have to stay between 0 and 9. You can see your current value by looking at the addition signs filling up the squares on your character cube.</i><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Want to learn even more?</h2></strong><br><br>Mighty Math is a mind bending fusion of arcade survival and brain training all in one. Anyone can pick it up and play. It starts with a simple premise, collect a required set of numbers before all numbers run out to survive each round. As you collect numbers you will change the player value. You must maintain a player value between 0 and 9. If you go over or under this value range you will be instantly destroyed.<br><br>Although the game starts off with a simple concept, it contains endless rounds and ramps up in difficulty immensely. Survive as long as you can to set high scores to share with your friends!<br><br>Enjoy wild randomized runs with varying sets of numbers and traps for a unique experience each run!<br><br>Train your brain as you survive the mathematical onslaught in Mighty Math!",
